abstract.para: This dataset contains meteorological, phenological, and chemical data collected from shrimp ecosystems, with a focus on temperature, rainfall, solar radiation, and various chemical measurements. Data spans from 1975 to 2024, with several gaps and missing data points.

description.para: Data was collected using standard meteorological and chemical monitoring techniques. Temperature and rainfall were recorded daily, while chemical measurements were collected at regular intervals depending on site conditions.
